Add function to convert arrays to Benjamin arrays.

Add template for custom routing-instances on cloudsw

Patch adds new vars to be added to define VRFs and their assciated
IDs, as well as place specific interfaces on devices into those VRFs
(routing instances).

Does not use 'replace' for the whole routing-instance stanza, to
facilitate protocols to be configured in it manually for the time
being.

Also includes changes / vars for the new cloudsw in rows E/F and
the existing ones to move the new xlink irb sub-ints to vrf 'cloud',
which will be required for the migration and also gives an example
of how it would be used.

Diff on current cloudsw: https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/P27958

different ideas about monitoring external vs internal certs,
different ideas _where_ to add the monitoring code,
probably makes sense to leave it to general discussion
between observability and traffic because we have been going
back and forth and while I have time to fix it for _one service_ I feel
related to I don't have the time to start the general discussion
for monitoring of all services.
